PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Employment and Social Development of VICTOR BRUNETTE of Gatineau, Quebec, to be a member of the Board of Directors of the National Capital Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Richard Paul Jennings.
